title: Ep. - 457 - RETIRED FBI AGENT DISCUSSES SHERRI PAPINI UNSOLVED CASE WITH JONATHAN MARK
description:
Kate discusses this week’s most talked about episode of The Bachelor.

 

Retired FBI agent Jennifer Coffindaffer discusses the case of Sherri Papini, a California woman accused of staging her own 2016 kidnapping. 

 

Medium Jonathan Mark helps Kate help a listener’s request to find answers to her brother-in-law’s mysterious death.
